Business Understanding

You now understand:

ERP integrates all departments into one system.
Odoo is a complete ERP platform with multiple business applications.
A Functional Consultant focuses on business processes, configuration, documentation, testing, and user training.
Different departments (Sales, Purchase, Inventory, HR, Accounting, etc.) work together using a centralized database.
Odoo can be a suitable ERP solution for businesses that need more than accounting software.
